version_description: The Fox Business app for iOS has been completely redesigned!
Various enhancements.
The Fox Business app for iOS has been completely redesigned!
Various enhancements.

- iPhone Xs (XR, Max) support
- Improved multitasking for iPad
- Major performance and functionality improvements
We're making continuous performance, reliability and feature improvements.
Bug fixes and visual improvements.
Introducing the all-new, redesigned Fox Business iOS app!

We update the Fox Business app regularly to introduce new features, performance enhancements, and reliability improvements.

In this release:
(+) Bug Fixes

We value your feedback, so if you run into any issues or have suggestions don't hesitate to reach out to us! Connect with us here: https://help.foxbusiness.com/
